title: Computer Shipments Sink Under Weight of Strong Dollar
text: October 08, 2015 at 18:16 PM EDT Computer Shipments Sink Under Weight of Strong Dollar A total of 73.7 million personal computers were shipped during the third quarter of the year, a number that includes desktop, laptop and notebook computers, and is down 7.7% from the same time last year. read more
